  "title": "Singapore Multi-Platform Local News Journalist, Lianhe Zaobao (采访组多平台记者,联合早报）",
  "description": "<p><strong>The Role</strong></p>\n<p>We are looking for journalists who are interested in what impacts daily lives in Singapore and around the world. You will be there there for our readers, witnessing significant events as they unfold, and be part of publishing the first draft of history.Your stories will also be published across Lianhe Zaobao's print, online and social media channels.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>一面工作一面学习，开拓视野同时开创事业。如果你对身边的小事特别敏锐，对国家大事特别好奇，喜欢说故事，那你在新闻室里将如鱼得水。你的新闻将通过《联合早报》纸媒、数码和社媒平台传播。</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Effectively bilingual in Chinese and English, with strong written and spoken skills as this is for a Chinese publication</li>\n  <li>Outgoing, independent and enjoys working in a dynamic environment that is non-desk bound</li>\n  <li>Analytical, inquisitive and good at asking \"why\"</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated, organized, able to work under pressure and think on your feet, and have an eye for details</li>\n  <li>Degree in any discipline; relevant experience as a journalist or video producer would be advantageous</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>兼通中英文，写作和表达能力强</li>\n  <li>不甘于成天对着电脑，喜欢与人交流，能独立外出采访</li>\n  <li>分析能力强，有好奇心，懂得问 “为什么”</li>\n  <li>面对压力沉着应对，临场反应好</li>\n  <li>能主动找新闻，善于观察，重视细节</li>\n  <li>有大学学历但专业不拘; 有采访和视频编导经验为佳，但不是必须</li>\n</ul>",
